WRATH
<ol><li> Who did you last get angry with? <br>
Someone on the road. 
<li> What is your weapon of choice? <br>
On the road?  I always have this urge to toss pennies at drivers who piss me off.  Otherwise?  A pool cue is the weapon that I actually used on someone most recently. 
<li> Would you hit a member of the opposite sex? <br>
I have, and it's one of my biggest regrets in my life.  I intend never to do so again. 
<li> How about of the same sex? <br>
Yes.  But I would need to be really angry. 
<li> Who was the last person that got really angry at you? <br>
Probably my father. 
<li> What is your pet peeve? <br>
Having to wait. 
<li> Do you keep grudges, or can you let them go easily? <br>
Depends on the situation.  
</ol>

SLOTH
