Stephanie, although I call her on occasion, and she never calls me back. 
<li> What is the last lame excuse you've made? <br>
I'm tired. 
<li> Have you ever watched an infomercial all the way through? <br>
Yes.  For Auri, the car polish.  
<li> When was the last time you got a good workout in? <br>
Last Friday.  
<li> How many times did you hit the snooze button on your alarm clock today? <br>
None--I usually set the alarm for an hour earlier than I need to get up and then listen to the radio. 
</ol>

