Of course. 
<li> Have you wanted someone who was taken? <br>
All the time. 
<li> What is your favorite body part on a person of your gender of choice? <br>
The center of the back, where the muscles dip into the spine. 
<li> Have you ever been propositioned by a prostitute? <br>
Propositioned by?  Yes. 
<li> Have you ever had a one night stand? <br>
